{"lemma":"طَبْعُ","slug":"طَبْعُ","root":"ط.ب.ع","root_slug":"ط-ب-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ب-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طَبْعُ","root":"طبع","pos":"V","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26313","n26314","n26318","n26319","n26320","n26321"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to print, imprint, stamp"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to type"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to coin"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to train, to tame (an animal)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to train, to teach (someone)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to normalize (relations)","examples":[{"text":"طَبَّعَتِ الدَوْلَتانِ عَلاقَاتِهِمَا الدِبْلُوماسِيّة.","english":"The two countries normalized their diplomatic relations."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to embellish (fabric) when printing"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to defile"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَبَعَ (ṭabaʕa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"printing, print"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"nature"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"characteristic"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26313","headword_ar":"طَبَعَ","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sealed, stamped, imprinted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impressed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatama","text_ar":"خَتَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) [and, as now used,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he printed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a book or the like:]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboEN","text_ar":"تَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatomN","text_ar":"خَتْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"both signify the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making an impression"},{"kind":"text","text":"in, or upon, clay and the like: (S, Mgh, O, K:) or, as Er-Rághib says, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impressing"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the engraving of the signet and stamp:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xtm","text_ar":"ختم"},{"kind":"text","text":": [see more in the first paragraph of the latter art:]) and he says also that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figuring"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with some particular figure;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the case of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboE","text_ar":"طَبْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the die for stamping coins, and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboE","text_ar":"طَبْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"of coins [themselves]: but that it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more general in signification than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatomN","text_ar":"خَتْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more particular than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqo$N","text_ar":"نَقْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as will be shown by what follows: accord. to Aboo-Is-hák the Grammarian,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatomN","text_ar":"خَتْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"both signify the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering over"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and securing oneself from a thing's entering"},{"kind":"text","text":"it: and IAth says [in like manner] that they held"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayonN","text_ar":"رَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAna","text_ar":"رَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but Mujáhid says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rayonN","text_ar":"رَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"denotes less than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", less than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iqofaAlN","text_ar":"اـِقْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or the “ closing with a lock: ” this he says with reference to a phrase in the Kur xlvii. 26]. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa AlkitaAba","text_ar":"طَبَعَ الكِتَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa EalaY","text_ar":"طَبَعَ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkitaAbi","text_ar":"الكِتَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatama","text_ar":"خَتَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, Mgh, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa","text_ar":"طَبَعَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He branded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"otherwise marked, the sheep,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbaEN","text_ar":"طَابَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa A@ll~`hu EalaY qalobihi","text_ar":"طَبَعَ ا@للّٰهُ عَلَى قَلْبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God sealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set a seal upon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. an unbeliever's]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heart, so that he should not heed admonition, nor be disposed to that which is good;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that belief should not enter it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) [and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xatama Ealayohi","text_ar":"خَتَمَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.:] in this, regard is had to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboE","text_ar":"طَبْع"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiyEap","text_ar":"طَبِيعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the natural constitution or disposition; for it denotes the characterizing of the soul with some particular quality or qualities, either by creation or by habit, and more especially by creation. (Er-Rághib, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He began to make,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manufacture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing] as in instances here following. (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa mina AlT~iyni","text_ar":"طَبَعَ مِنَ الطِّينِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jar~apF","text_ar":"جَرَّةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fashioned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moulded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the clay, a jar."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa All~abina","text_ar":"طَبَعَ اللَّبِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ayofa","text_ar":"السَّيْفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~irohamu","text_ar":"الدِّرْهَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, O, K) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the crude bricks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sword,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dirhem"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa","text_ar":"طَبَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~araAhima","text_ar":"الدَّرَاهِمَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the die"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coined,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"minted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dirhems,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"money."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.) And [hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tabaqahu A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"طَبَقَهُ ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AlA^amori","text_ar":"عَلَى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God created him with an adaptation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disposition, to the thing, affair, state, condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adapted him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed him, by creation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nature"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereto."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TubiEa EalaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"طُبِعَ عَلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, O, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was created with an adaptation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disposition, to the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was adapted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disposed, by creation"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nature"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereto;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubila","text_ar":"جُبِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IDrd, O, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuTira","text_ar":"فُطِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lh, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, (aor. as above, TA, and so the inf. n., O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He filled"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, O, K, TA) a measure for corn or the like, (Er-Rághib, TA,) or a leathern bucket, (O, K, TA,) and a skin, (O, TA,) &c.; (O;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tb~E","text_ar":"طبّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTobiyEN","text_ar":"تَطْبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) because the quantity that fills it is a sign that prevents the taking a portion of what is in it [without the act's being discovered]. (Er-Rághib, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEa qafaAhu","text_ar":"طَبَعَ قَفَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, O, K,) inf. n. as above, (IAar, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck the back of his neck with his hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K;) i. e. the back of the neck of a boy: if with the ends of the fingers, one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qa*~a qafaAhu","text_ar":"قَذَّ قَفَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IAar, O.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^adoriY mino A^ayona TabaEa","text_ar":"مَا اَدْرِى مِنْ اَيْنَ طَبَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I know not whence he came forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaEa","text_ar":"طَلَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiEa","text_ar":"طَبِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEN","text_ar":"طَبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a sword,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, rusty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overspread with rust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very rusty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overspread with much rust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA: from an explanation of the aor.: but this is written in the CK and in my MS. copy of the K, and in the O,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuTobaEu","text_ar":"يُطْبَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". [An explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEN","text_ar":"طَبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the O and K confirms the reading"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaTobaEu","text_ar":"يَطْبَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and another confirmation thereof will be found in what follows in this paragraph.]) ―         -b2-  Said of a thing, (Msb,) or of a garment, or piece of cloth, (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEN","text_ar":"طَبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dirty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tT~bE","text_ar":"تطّبع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is likewise said [in the same sense] of a garment, or piece of cloth. (M and TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAna","text_ar":"رَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ryn","text_ar":"رين"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  Said of a man, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, filthy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in character"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, sluggish, lazy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indolent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) One says of a man,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaTobaEu","text_ar":"يَطْبَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaforaHu","text_ar":"يَفْرَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has no penetrative energy, sharpness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effectiveness, in the affairs that are the means,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causes, of attaining honour, like the sword that is overspread with much rust."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TubiEa","text_ar":"طُبِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) said of a man, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was rendered"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in character"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O, K;) on the authority of Sh; (O;) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiEa","text_ar":"طَبِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA as on the authority of Sh; [but this I think doubtful;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and disgraced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishonoured:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tub~iEa","text_ar":"طُبِّعَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTobiyEN","text_ar":"تَطْبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was rendered"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in character"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and blamed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discommended."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","Mgh","O","K","TA","IDrd","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n26314","headword_ar":"طبّع","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTobiyEN","text_ar":"تَطْبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sealed well"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sealed"},{"kind":"text","text":"a number of writings &c.]. (KL: in which only the inf. n. is mentioned.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He loaded"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a beast"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heavily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) ―         -b3-  See also 1, a little after the middle.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTobiyEN","text_ar":"تَطْبِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendering unclean, dirty, filthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b2-  See 1, last sentence."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n26318","headword_ar":"طَبْعٌ","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", originally an inf. n., (S,) signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A nature;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a natural, a native,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an innate, disposition"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"temper"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an idiosyncrasy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sajiy~apN","text_ar":"سَجِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~apN","text_ar":"جِبِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaliyqapN","text_ar":"خَلِيقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to which a man is adapted by creation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K, TA;) [as though it were stamped, or impressed, upon him;] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiyEapN","text_ar":"طَبِيعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K, TA;) or this signifies his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mizaAj","text_ar":"مِزَاج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constitution,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"temperament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aggregate natural constituents"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"humours;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb; [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mizaAjN","text_ar":"مِزَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TibaAEN","text_ar":"طِبَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K, TA;) or this last signifies, (K,) or signifies also, (O,) with the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are, constituted in us in consequence of food and drink &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA ruk~iba fiynaA","text_ar":"مَا رُكِّبَ فِينَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlmaToEami waAlma$orabi wagoyari *`lika","text_ar":"مِنَ المَطْعَمِ وَالمَشْرَبِ وَغْيَرِ ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mTEm","text_ar":"مطعم"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m$rb","text_ar":"مشرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"are evidently used as inf. ns. agreeably with general analogy]), (O, K, TA,) by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyr *lk","text_ar":"غير ذلك"},{"kind":"text","text":"being meant"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as straitness and ampleness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of circumstances"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and niggardliness and liberality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the natural dispositions that are inseparable from us;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) and this word is fem., (O, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiyEapN","text_ar":"طَبِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as is said in the M; or it is sing. and masc. accord. to Abu-l-Kásim Ez-Zejjájee; and it is also pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaboEN","text_ar":"طَبْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as it is said to be by Az; (TA;) [and those who have asserted it to be fem. may have held it to be a pl.;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAbiEN","text_ar":"طَابِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TibaAEN","text_ar":"طِبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as a sing.]; (K, TA;) or, as Lh says, it is syn. with ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiyEapN","text_ar":"طَبِيعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaAy^iEu","text_ar":"طَبَايِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Model, make, fashion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mould:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiDoribohu EalaY TaboEi h`*aA","text_ar":"اِضْرِبْهُ عَلَى طَبْعِ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make thou it, fashion it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mould it, according to the model, make, fashion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mould, of this"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, O, L, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n26319","headword_ar":"طِبْعٌ","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A river,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rivulet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, T, S, O, K, TA;) so called because"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first dug"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and filled"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"having the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTobuwEN","text_ar":"مَطْبُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qTofN","text_ar":"قطْفٌ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1824},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoTuwfN","text_ar":"مَقْطُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; not applied to any of those cleft by God, such as the Tigris and the Euphrates and the Nile and the like thereof: (Az, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaAEN","text_ar":"اَطْبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly a pl. of pauc.,] (As, S, O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TubuwEN","text_ar":"طُبُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as heard by Az from the Arabs, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TibaAEN","text_ar":"طِبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~iboEu","text_ar":"الطِّبْعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as some say, is the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a particular river:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or it is also thus applied, i. e. to a particular river. (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magiyDu maA='K","text_ar":"مَغِيضُ مَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place where water sinks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goes away, into the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where water enters into the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where it collects"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaAEN","text_ar":"اَطْبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, TA.) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity sufficient for the filling of a measure for corn or the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA, ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wAls~iqA='u","text_ar":"والسِّقا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the CK being a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAls~iqaA='i","text_ar":"وَالسِّقَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as does not admit of any addition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity that a vessel holds, of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["Az","TA","As","S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26320","headword_ar":"طَبَعٌ","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirtiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiboEN","text_ar":"طِبْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rustiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon iron;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirtiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering the sword:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much dirtiness"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirt, from rust:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTobaAEN","text_ar":"اَطْبَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabiEa","text_ar":"طَبِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TabaEN","text_ar":"طَبَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the inf. n.]) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disgrace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dishonour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, O, K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiyoEN","text_ar":"طِيْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in religion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of worldly things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, TA.) Thábit-Kutneh says, in a verse ascribed by Et-Tanookhee to 'Orweh Ibn-Udheyneh,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laA xayora fiY TamaEK yahodiY A_ilaY TabaEK\n                      \n                     \n                        waguf~apN mino qiwaAmi AlEayo$i takofiyniY"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no good in coveting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covetousness, that leads to disgrace: and a sufficiency of the means of subsistence contents me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yahodiY","text_ar":"يَهْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this case means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^ad~iY","text_ar":"يُوَدِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","O","K","TA","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n26321","headword_ar":"طَبِعٌ","root":"TbE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rusty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a sword. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  Applied to a man, (O,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Filthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul, base, ignoble, mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sordid, in disposition; that will not be ashamed of an evil action"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sluggish, lazy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indolent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O"]}]}}